          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1715602855834-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer 1/3 of the <strong>chipotle sauce</strong> to a medium-sized pot – this is your<strong> enchilada topping</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> drained black beans</strong>, <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan with the <strong>remaining chipotle sauce </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>enchilada filling</strong></p><p>Return the pot with the<strong> enchilada topping</strong> to a high heat for 2-3 min or until the sauce has thickened to a double cream consistency</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1715602852190-x200.jpg",
